title: BONUS: Game of Roses Crossover Event!
itunes:title: BONUS: Game of Roses Crossover Event!
description:
Danny is wrapping up his book tour, but we have a special bonus chat with Chad & Lizzy, the hosts of the Game of Roses Bachelor podcast. They talk reality TV history, Bachelor Nation, and so much more!


Check out their book, How to Win the Bachelor: The Secret to Finding Love and Fame on America's Favorite Reality Show, out now!


TOUR TICKETS: https://everythingiconic.com/live-shows
